Package: GADES
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2026-07-10
Title: Hobotnica-GPU Lab-Medvedeva
Description: Parallel pairwise distance matrices for single-cell RNA sequencing
    data on GPU (CUDA) and CPU. Supports dense and sparse inputs and six metrics
    (euclidean, cosine, pearson, spearman, kendall, manhattan).
Author: Ausaaf Nabi <nabi.a@phystech.edu>, Akhatyamov Pavel <akhtyamovpavel@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Ausaaf Nabi <nabi.a@phystech.edu>
License: CC 3.0
Imports:
    Matrix,
    glue,
    methods
Suggests:
    hdf5r
SystemRequirements: OpenBLAS; CUDA toolkit + cuBLAS (optional, for the GPU
    backend; the CPU backend builds and runs without CUDA); CMake (>= 3.10)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.2
